  "prompt": "A clean, high-resolution, stylized magical sigil on a black background. The sigil is gold and symmetrical, combining elements of angelic and demonic symbolism. It features a central vertical axis like a spine, two upward arched horns or wings, a circular enclosure with intersecting lines forming an 'X', and a base with a downward-pointing triangle or arrow. The design should evoke a fusion of Samael (left-hand path, rebellion, fire) and Metatron (divine structure, geometry, order). The style is mystical, occult, and elegant, suitable for use as a standalone ritual seal or vector.",
